rComments: I think the professor is very kind and approachable when responding to questions and clarifications. However, I find her rubrics for group projects very confusing which is stressful because group work in that class is worth 50% of your mark. The bottom line is if you get a bad group your overall grade is heavily impacted.
What a nice woman! Easy class, make sure you have a good group of group members. Prof makes the class very enjoyable and is extremely sweet and willing to go above and beyond for students.
